OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPublic sector pay increase 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmust be responsible - PM   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Rishi Sunak has said he would make the 
OL,6, "responsible" decision on pay increases
OL,7, for public sector workers, in order to 
OL,8, control inflation.                     
OL,10,FMinisters have confirmed they are now  
OL,11,Fconsidering next year's pay deal, after
OL,12,Fseveral independent pay review bodies  
OL,13,Freported their findings.               
OL,15,FMr Sunak said he was going to make the 
OL,16,F"right" decisions "for the country".   
OL,18,FBut government sources warn ministers  
OL,19,Fwould not be prepared to increase      
OL,20,Fborrowing to fund generous awards.     
